examples.en: Tax is payable on the interest.
The rent is payable in advance.
The check was marked “payable to bearer.”
examples.ru: На чеке было написано: “К оплате предъявителю”.

examples.en: The mortgage is payable in monthly instalments.
Cheques should be made payable to the National Trust.
examples.ru: Чеки должны быть выписаны на имя Национального фонда.
